[
  {
    "p": "Notes/Getting Things Done.md",
    "t": "Getting Things Done",
    "ex": "...a system for productivity and...",
    "mc": 5,
    "ln": 3
  },
  {
    "p": "Books/Deep Work.md",
    "t": "Deep Work",
    "ex": "...focus and productivity in...",
    "mc": 4,
    "ln": 12
  }
]
\`\`\`

ðŸ”§ MCP-Obsidian: Using read_multiple_notes...

